TaggedPlayerRoundHand = (PlayerRoundHand, PlayerCall, PlayerWon: bool)
PlayerRoundHand:
    GT Hand: Hand
    Hand Pre exch: Hand
    Hand post exch: Hand
    => 24 Byte
    fn weggeschupft -> Hand
    fn zugeschupft -> Hand
Round:
 4 PlayerRoundHands 24 Bytes each
 Player Calls - 1 Byte
 Player Positions - 1 Byte
 Card Score - 1 Byte
 5 padding bytes
 => 104 Bytes per round

 Game:
    Vec<Round>
    Vec<RoundLog>
    playerid: 2 Byte each

    160 Byte* rounds + 8 Byte
    => Around 3.37 GB (should implement serialization/de-serialization).
 TaggedCardIndex: 2 Bits Player, 6 Bits CardIndex
    fn get_player, fn get_card_index -> Trait again Ig
 RoundLog:
    Vec<TaggedCardIndex: u8> -> 56 Byte per Round
